Label: # Resident Variance
Description: A count of residents with a variance between their assessed and billed care.

Label: Upcoming Assessments
Description: A count of resident assessments occurring in the next 7 days.

Label: Variance Age
Description: # of days between assessed effective date and billed effective date.

Label: Pending Assessments
Description: A count of assessments that have not yet been submitted.

Label: % Past Due Assessments
Def: [# of Past Due Assessments] / [# of Residents]
DefExpanded: [# of Past Due Assessments] / [# of Residents]
Description: The percentage of assessments that are past due.
MeasureNames: # of Past Due Assessments, # of Residents

Label: % Residents Change in Care Level CHART
Def: [# Residents Change in Care]  / Count(distinct TOTAL [%CustomerIDKey])
DefExpanded: [# Residents Change in Care]  / Count(distinct TOTAL [%CustomerIDKey])
Description: The percent of residents that have had a change in care level in the trailing twelve months.

Label: % Residents with Change in Care Level
Def: [# Residents Change in Care] /  [# of Residents]
DefExpanded: [# Residents Change in Care] /  [# of Residents]
Description: The percentage of residents that have had a change in care level in the trailing year.
MeasureNames: # Residents Change in Care, # of Residents

Label: Residents on STL
Description: A count of residents on short term leave-- with no actual return date on record.

Label: Residents with Ancillary Variance
Description: Residents with variance between their assessed ancillary care and their billed ancillary care.

Label: # Changes in Care
Description: A count of care level changes occurring in the trailing twelve months.

Label: Residents with Primary Variance
Description: A count of residents with a variance in their assessed primary care and their  billed primary care

Label: Next Assessment Date
Description: The date of the resident's next assessment.

Label: Changes in Care
Description: A count of instances that residents have had a change in care level. Trailing 12 months.

Label: Days to Next Assessment
Description: The total number of days between 8/2/2022 and the next assessment date.

Label: # Residents Change in Care
Description: A count of residents that have had a change in care level in the trailing year.

Label: # of Past Due Assessments
Description: Residents with a "Next Assessment Date" occurring before 8/2/2022

Label: Care Changes Pivot
Description: The amount of times a resident's care level has changed, and the date of the change.
